ng this warrior to 65 and am now ready to start the AAs. <br>
<br>
Ever since I raided with my monk and saw the flurry attacks from Vindi and mobs of the like, I have SO wanted to see:<br>
<br>
Angre executes a FLURRY of attack's on TARGET!<br>
<br>
So now I find out that no one gets to see this message but me when I  flurry. Is it me, or does this seem like total bullshit.<br>
I think we should start a petition that makes rampage and flurry by PCs be saw by everyone.<br>
<br>
Thoughts???<br>
<br>
<br>
EDIT: For the Raaj <p><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://home.attbi.com/~bragalus/wsb/media/61745/site1021.jpg" style="border:0;"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--></div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=435743" target="top">Angre Scottishguy</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--></div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center">Overlord of Halas</div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center">Baron of the Wolves</div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center">Officer of Untamed Souls</div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior.showUserPublicProfile?gid=angrescottishguy>Angre Scottishguy</A> at: 4/15/03 7:07:47 am<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2F2F4F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior.showUserPublicProfile?gid=raaj>Raaj</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>will kick your @$$</span><br>  Posts: 633<br> <font color=#FF0000>(4/14/03 4:33:26 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthetavern.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2068.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Rant About Flurry</span><hr size=1> <!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>I think we should start a petition that makes rampage and flurry by NPCs be saw by everyone.<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
