<!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.clantaveren.com" target="top">Clan Ta Veren</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior.showUserPublicProfile?gid=kirle>Kirle</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>/cons RED</span><br>  Posts: 344<br> <font color=#FF0000>(4/14/03 6:43:48 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthetavern.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2068.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Rant About Flurry</span><hr size=1> Why?  I know it seems like a big thing but it will just be something that people will filter out so they don't have to see.  Not to belittle the acomplishment, but Isn't you seeing it satisfaction enough? <p><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><br>
Kirle Koward<br>
61 Warlord<br>
<!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=215801" target="top">Stuff No One Else Wanted</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
</div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--><br>
</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2F2F4F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior.showUserPublicProfile?gid=karleafv>KarleaFV</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>knows that Warriors are superior</span><br>  Posts: 6<br> <font color=#FF0000>(4/14/03 11:36:04 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthetavern.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2068.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Rant About Flurry</span><hr size=1> I agree with Angre, I really hoped everyon would see the message too, and if it's only to look a bit &quot;uber&quot;. But all in all it's just a minor thing, nothing worth to waste any energy getting angry over for. <p><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://eqsigs.screamparks.net/images/hosted/Karlea.jpg"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--></div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--><br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong><!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=215107">Touch the lizard!</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--></div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--></em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--></strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior.showUserPublicProfile?gid=harbromme>Harbromme</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>knows that Warriors are superior</span><br>  Posts: 55<br> <font color=#FF0000>(4/15/03 12:18:18 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthetavern.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2068.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Rant About Flurry</span><hr size=1> I have other melee messages filtered off all the time, including crit hits and blasts.<br>
Spam in raid encounters is bad enough as it is, so why bother with more messages to be filtered out. <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=65418">Gnomb Goodbasher level 65 troll warrior</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
<!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.divinelegend.com">Divine Legend - Terris Thule</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2F2F4F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior.showUserPublicProfile?gid=wubaogoldenarmz>Wubao Goldenarmz</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>will kick your @$$</span><br>  Posts: 542<br> <font color=#FF0000>(4/15/03 2:05:45 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthetavern.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2068.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   eye candy</span><hr size=1> It wouldn't be eye candy if everyone filtered it all out.<br>
<br>
So, yeah, the AA would be cooler (and just a SMIDGE more worth the 18 AA levels of grinding to get) if it added to the spam.<br>
<br>
Sure people filter it out.<br>
<br>
But not everyone does.<br>
<br>
And seeing Soandso lands a flurry of attacks would be kinda neat every now and then.<br>
<br>
-Wubao <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior.showUserPublicProfile?gid=xeriea232>Xeriea232</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>knows that Warriors are superior</span><br>  Posts: 10<br> <font color=#FF0000>(4/15/03 5:42:23 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthetavern.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2068.topic&index=6>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: eye candy</span><hr size=1> Although it would be nice if everyone sees it, I would just be happy if I know it's actually working <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=223917" target="top">Taarna Sunseeker</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> - 65th Half Elf Overlord<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=51851" target="top">Xeriea Blackrose</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> - 64th Teir`Dal Phantasmist<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=595159" target="top">Nalevi</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> - 56th Fier`Dal Outrider</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2F2F4F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior.showUserPublicProfile?gid=farlanderb>FarlanderB</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>is a Formidable Opponent</span><br>  Posts: 128<br> <font color=#FF0000>(4/15/03 5:52:44 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthetavern.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2068.topic&index=7>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: eye candy</span><hr size=1> I think it would be cool if everyone saw it. Ah well, I guess I'll just make an emote to click everytime I flurry.<br>
<br>
/em Farlander executes a FLURRY of attacks on Target. <br>
<br>
hehe =) <p>- <!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=607776">Far</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior.showUserPublicProfile?gid=angrescottishguy>Angre Scottishguy</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>knows that Warriors are superior</span><br>  Posts: 17<br> <font color=#FF0000>(4/15/03 8:14:44 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthetavern.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2068.topic&index=8>Reply</a>    <br>ezSupporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: eye candy</span><hr size=1> Eye candy is always nice. Let's face it, us warriors don't get much fluff in the game. We take a beating and we give one back. Sometimes we get nice looking crits and crips but that is about it.<br>
<br>
I just would like to see something that defines the class a little bit to others. <br>
<br>
I agree that me knowing is prolly enough but 18AA's is a lot to spend not to get a little treat for it. <p><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://home.attbi.com/~bragalus/wsb/media/61745/site1021.jpg" style="border:0;"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--></div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=435743" target="top">Angre Scottishguy</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--></div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center">Overlord of Halas</div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center">Baron of the Wolves</div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center">Officer of Untamed Souls</div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2F2F4F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior.showUserPublicProfile?gid=solinarinnoruuk>Solinar Innoruuk</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>will kick your @$$</span><br>  Posts: 434<br> <font color=#FF0000>(4/16/03 8:30:23 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthetavern.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2068.topic&index=9>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re:</span><hr size=1> It would just add to spam, like crits, so no I wouldnt want it to be visible to all.<br>
<br>
Trust me, people notice.  I cant tell you how many times casters or debuffers in my guild have sent me a tell while I was tanking somthing big to the tune of &quot;I love it when you tank&quot; or &quot;your the only one I can chain nuke with&quot;.<br>
<br>
If you get good aggro weps (I use bloodfrenzy and BoC still) and fully maxxed offensive AA, trust me, casters will notice. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthetavern.showPrevMessage?topicID=2068.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthetavern.showNextMessage?topicID=2068.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthetavern.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2068.topic&index=9><img src=http://www.steelwarrior.org/forum/swaddreply.GIF border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthetavern.emailToFriend?topicID=2068.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthetavern.threadControl?topicID=2068.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthetavern.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=2068.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthetavern.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=2068.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub14.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="thesteelwarriorthearena">The Arena<option value="thesteelwarriorthebattlefield">The BattleField<option value="thesteel